{"tid":675393,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【一分鐘粵語】失魂魚即係乜魚？總有一條喺左近","createTime":"2018-05-23T13:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T12:11:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"68bb9cc0d156bda368c216305bed996f1f820570","tid":675393,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:02:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20180522/20397685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F20397685&d=vpYrFJbs0IQmUCDlfh9O0Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=cf4002ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F20397685&h=7f66b244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20180522/20397685</a><br />\n<br />\n【一分鐘粵語】失魂魚即係乜魚？總有一條喺左近<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180522/large/sub39001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180522%2Flarge%2Fsub39001.jpg&h=9ea3aff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每個office都總有幾條失魂魚，你我或者都比人話得多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每個office都總有幾條失魂魚，你我或者都比人話得多。小時候總以為，失魂魚是餸菜名，不然怎會次次被話後，當晚都有魚食，當然後來發現，兩者純屬巧合。究竟失魂魚的前身是甚麼？根據蘇萬興編著的《老餅潮語III》，失魂魚指冒失、精神不集中的人，中晒？恭喜你，歡迎加入這個海洋家族。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180522/large/sub39001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180522%2Flarge%2Fsub39001.jpg&h=9ea3aff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n漁民會將魚類養在魚排，到出售時才撈起。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一直以來，漁民會將捕捉回來的魚類，先養在魚排，出售時才會撈起，並放入較小的魚缸，再用車或船運到市場。不過，這些魚本身習慣在魚排及魚塘中生活，轉了新環境，多數不太適應；<br />\n再加上，在運送過程中，車船不停搖晃，對比起水流較靜的魚排，魚缸內的水顯然波動得多，有如「暈車浪」及「暈船浪」，所以當魚類到達目的地時，早已反應遲鈍，不肯動，被稱之為「失魂」。後來，大家就將這個狀態，去形容做事三魂唔見七魄的人了。<br />\n<br />\n記者：湯珮然<br />\n攝影：蕭志南、張志孟<br />\n<br />\n全新旅遊專頁，即like籽想旅行：<a href=\"https://fb.com/travel.appleseed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Ftravel.appleseed&d=vpYrFJbs0IQmUCDlfh9O0Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=33fed669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/travel.appleseed</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【有故事的人】角落裏奏曼陀鈴　悼念永遠9歲的兒子"},{"pid":"d1707fae3d6a2831bd9e234c7182ccc0cdadfa9e","tid":675393,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.gamersky.com/showimage/id_gamersky.shtml?http://img1.gamersky.com/image2016/06/20160626_gxh_289_9/image001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamersky.com%2Fshowimage%2Fid_gamersky.shtml%3Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2016%2F06%2F20160626_gxh_289_9%2Fimage001.jpg&h=8a737927&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93b60cee02f9ad6d4a1d74e1f970f60f36cb35a8","tid":675393,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2016/06/20160626_gxh_289_9/image001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2016%2F06%2F20160626_gxh_289_9%2Fimage001.jpg&h=1b030bb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e805ba54941fd908076f9b8f4b1e51f8567ff200","tid":675393,"uid":29940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"咁 失"}]}